    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hell Division</strong> 是一款第三人称射击游戏，您将操控一架战斗无人机，在高科技世界中展开激烈的空中战斗。使用各种武器类型，摧毁敌人，探索未来主义风格的战斗场景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>关于本游戏</strong><br>这是一款快节奏的动作射击游戏，主角是一架配备枪械的军用无人机。您将沉浸于赛博朋克氛围中，亲历两个强大企业之间的战争。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2004360/extras/36f0970cb2d0d666a0a39b295e6e12ce.poster.avif?t=1755954582\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2004360/extras/36f0970cb2d0d666a0a39b295e6e12ce.webm?t=1755954582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2004360/extras/36f0970cb2d0d666a0a39b295e6e12ce.mp4?t=1755954582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>背景故事</strong><br>一开始，一家强大的无人机制造公司几乎掌控了整个网络空间，意图制定自己的规则、主宰一切。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2004360/extras/2d3cb9aa3875310d8abf9bad5c2f5d06.poster.avif?t=1755954582\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2004360/extras/2d3cb9aa3875310d8abf9bad5c2f5d06.webm?t=1755954582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2004360/extras/2d3cb9aa3875310d8abf9bad5c2f5d06.mp4?t=1755954582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>平衡力量</strong><br>但事情并不简单。另一家公司推出了性能更强的无人机，虽然数量远不如对手，但实力不容小觑。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2004360/extras/d9032edffd6e471b906be5f8deb71d17.poster.avif?t=1755954582\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2004360/extras/d9032edffd6e471b906be5f8deb71d17.webm?t=1755954582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2004360/extras/d9032edffd6e471b906be5f8deb71d17.mp4?t=1755954582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你将成为关键</strong><br>您将操控这种先进无人机，面对几十架敌方单位。任务艰巨，需要战术才能取胜。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2004360/extras/c86713a84c41afbccd14212be4d82ee3.poster.avif?t=1755954582\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2004360/extras/c86713a84c41afbccd14212be4d82ee3.webm?t=1755954582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2004360/extras/c86713a84c41afbccd14212be4d82ee3.mp4?t=1755954582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 个赛博朋克风格的地图</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于两大公司对抗的剧情</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动态空战体验</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精细的敌方 AI</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种任务类型</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各类难度的敌人</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >酷炫音轨</p></li></ul>",
